{"tid":2434151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女咖啡師控暴動縱火等罪 官准控方將粗口指罵警口供呈堂 下周一結案陳詞","createTime":"2021-03-05T10:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T13:15:03.000Z","uid":56115,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7d849c94b4dca72303767e38b90ab67214bbf6","tid":2434151,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"示威者前年9月底在旺角警署外縱火堵路，事後有年輕女咖啡師在私家車上遇警截查，其間被指曾稱：「<span class=\"red\">我頭先喺旺角警署出面屌完差人</span>，見到差人出嚟，驚咪走囉。」女咖啡師否認暴動及縱火等罪，並反對將控方所稱的說話內容呈堂。惟法官姚勳智今裁定相關口頭招認可以呈堂，亦裁定案件表證成立。案件將於下周一結案陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n被告面<span class=\"red\">對暴動、在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器及兩項縱火罪</span>，指她案發當日在旺角太子道西與彌敦道交界用火損毀他人財物、參與暴動，以及在太子道西無合法權限或辯解下管有雷射筆。"},{"pid":"fce44004950dba4393f4e0cf333fe1ed78b1730e","tid":2434151,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T10:25:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210305/VJH3CCBI4BDEPG63JAFHJYGOMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210305%2FVJH3CCBI4BDEPG63JAFHJYGOMU%2F&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=beebfb52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210305%2FVJH3CCBI4BDEPG63JAFHJYGOMU%2F&h=a23b7c1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210305/VJH3CCBI4BDEPG63JAFHJYGOMU/</a>"},{"pid":"a5cb1d1a29b8b750491b75278c453a724847546e","tid":2434151,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b69736c27e38b0279bb4b88805df021306bba9a","tid":2434151,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T10:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376a95a8b8b2d956ab481bbc883cf7afbe927